      <p style="font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.7;">When someone searches "best [your service] near me," Google shows three businesses above all other results. Those three businesses — the local 3-pack — get the majority of clicks, calls, and walk-ins. If your Google Business Profile is not optimized, you are not in that 3-pack. And every day you are not, your competitors are getting the customers that should be yours.</p>

      <p>Most business owners claim their Google Business Profile, add a phone number and maybe a photo, and never touch it again. That is not optimization — that is a placeholder. Google rewards profiles that are complete, active, and consistent. We make yours all three.</p>

      <p><strong>We set up, optimize, and manage your Google Business Profile so you show up when local customers are ready to buy.</strong></p>

