          <ul>
            <li>Claim, verify, or create your Google Business Profile</li>
            <li>Primary and secondary category strategy (critical for ranking)</li>
            <li>Business description optimized for search</li>
            <li>Complete service listings with keyword-rich descriptions</li>
            <li>Photo optimization — cover, logo, interior, exterior, team, products</li>
            <li>Attributes and amenities setup</li>
            <li>Q&A section populated with common customer questions</li>
            <li>Review response strategy and templates</li>
            <li>NAP consistency audit (Name, Address, Phone across the web)</li>
            <li>Citation building — directory listings that boost your authority</li>
            <li>Link your profile to your website, booking system, and menu (if applicable)</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="phase-note">Typically completed in 1-2 weeks. Custom quote based on your industry and current profile state.</div>
        </div>

