      <p style="text-align:center;color:#888;font-size:0.9rem;">Every business is different. We quote pricing after reviewing your profile, competition, and goals — so you get a plan that fits, not a one-size-fits-all package.</p>

      <h2>Why This Matters More Than You Think</h2>

      <p>Google Business Profile is the fastest path to local visibility for most businesses. It is free to have a profile, but without optimization and consistent activity, it does nothing for you. Here is what changes when it is done right:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>You show up in Google Maps</strong> when customers search for what you sell</li>
        <li><strong>You appear in the local 3-pack</strong> — the three results above all organic listings</li>
        <li><strong>Customers see your reviews, photos, and hours</strong> before they ever visit your website</li>
        <li><strong>You get direct calls, direction requests, and website clicks</strong> from the search results page itself</li>
        <li><strong>You build trust before the first conversation</strong> — a well-maintained profile signals a professional business</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Most of your competitors either have not set this up properly or set it up once and never touched it again. That is your advantage.</p>

